@prefix this: <https://w3id.org/np/RA15yj_WNnINHig5Sz87zdb34h19CsApQ-3FqOvymtYSo> .
@prefix sub: <https://w3id.org/np/RA15yj_WNnINHig5Sz87zdb34h19CsApQ-3FqOvymtYSo/> .
